snippet.title: Super Knight World Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The first official trailer for 'Super Knight World' a retro jump and run adventure coming to PC, Mac and Linux!
Check it out at http://coffeemuggames.itch.io/super-knight-world, read the devblog on http://indiedb.com/games/super-knight-world  or follow me on twitter.com/coffeemuggames
